<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und begert hat, daz wir den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> dem Prenher und dem Lomeir recht in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rat geen und
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>faren</expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, als wir vor <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und wenn sie oder ir
                                <expan>scheinbotte<ex>n</ex></expan> mit irem
                            <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt zu uns
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und des begern, so
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in gen <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und, der wir mechtig sein,
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> czu eren <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        recht in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rat geen und
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>faren</expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, so die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, zu
                        den sie zu <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan>, anheim sein, on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>d</expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
